title: FrischKostBar
typeOfFood: Organic, Raw, Western, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering
description: A vegetarian restaurant with vegan options. Serves a variety of fresh salads, sandwiches, soups, cakes, smoothies. Mostly raw. Has some tables and a bar. Everything is freshly made-in-house using only seasonal, locally grown produce. Uses alternative sweeteners, such as agave.
